cs.LG, cs.CL, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR 

The paper presents an algorithm for solving complex structured prediction problems in natural language, speech, computational biology, and vision. These areas are typically covered by the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and cryptography and security (cs.CR). However, since the paper focuses on the algorithmic aspect of solving these problems, cs.LG is the most likely sub-category, followed by cs.CL and cs.CV.
